{
  "chapter": 250,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十五章 古都临淄。项少龙随凤菲歌团抵达齐国都城临淄，肖月潭为他易容改扮，以沈良身份混在家将之中。田单亲自率众在码头迎接凤菲，项少龙小心躲避以免被认出。在前往听松别馆的马车上，肖月潭向项少龙介绍临淄城貌与稷下学宫，谈及稷下剑圣曹秋道的超然地位与恐怖剑术。抵达别馆后，项少龙以沈良身份与张泉接触，故意透露田单与仲孙龙两个对手的消息来试探张泉反应。张泉听闻仲孙龙介入后大为紧张，透露其放高利贷的狠辣手段。项少龙同时得知齐襄王年老糊涂、太子被废、仲孙龙举荐二王子田建的王位之争。雷允儿等家将请求上街游玩，项少龙批准后张泉担忧仲孙龙会借机生事，项少龙判断在凤菲演出前仲孙龙应会给齐王和田单面子。章末项少龙踏雪追出城门，深感已被卷入齐国王位之争的漩涡。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "看来你在这里相当受尊重。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这叫有心算无心，刚才我很留意田单，这家伙除凤菲外，像看不到其他人的样子。唉！他的样貌比上回见面时苍老很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大城共有八座城门，横贯东西的两条大街是东大街和西大街，纵贯南北的大道也有两条，就叫南大街和北大街，非常易记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "东西向两条大道和南北向两条大道交叉的区域，有小临淄之称，最是热闹繁荣，是来此者必游之地，今晚我带你去凑凑热闹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我不该这么抛头露面吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你愈是闪缩，愈惹人生疑，就算外人不觉，张泉和他的手下总会有人生疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "那就依你之言吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这些是富民的宅第，院落数重，瓦顶白墙，单层院落，与街巷联排的普通民居有很大的分别。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小临淄店铺林立，你能想出来的买卖在此应有尽有，该处的卜命师更是天下闻名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "稷下学宫在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "在城西稷门外，是座令人叹为观止的宏伟建筑，到这里来讲学、显扬学问的被尊为稷下先生，门徒则被称为稷下学士，人数达数千之多。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我也曾被请到那里传授曲乐、医药之学，所以才备受尊敬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "邹衍是否到了那里？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个我就不大清楚了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "能成稷下先生，都非同小可，其特出者均被奉为上大夫，可不治而论政，邹衍正是其中一人，我只要问问便可告诉你答案。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "曹秋道又是怎样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此人在齐国地位超然，是齐王的师父，公卿大臣见到他都要叩头请安。他独自居于稷下学宫外的一间小屋里，清茶淡饭。今年怕都该有五十岁了，但望之只像三十许的人，一般人想见到他都不容易。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此人的剑术已到了出神入化的境界，近年来少有与人动手，皆因根本没有胆敢挑战他的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "以前常有人向他挑战吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁能击败他，可登上稷下剑圣的宝座，立即名震天下。不过此人的剑从来不讲人情，战败者非死即伤，所以现在再没有人肯去比试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "我已套取珍贵的消息，假若张兄肯付订金，小弟可如实相告。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那就最好。不过我们的主子仍未抵此处，订金一事要稍迟两天，沈兄可否先透露少许？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "原来答应助她的人，竟就是刚才来接她去赴宴的相国田单，此人权倾齐国，很不好惹。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我自有分寸，不用怕他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "不过我们主人的对手除田单外，还有个非同小可的人，叫仲孙龙，张兄听过没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "这是大小姐亲口告诉我的。张兄该知在大梁时，仲孙龙曾来找过她，逼她下嫁，被拒后声言不惜一切也要把她弄到手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这消息非常重要，必须尽早通知主子，否则恐怕会横生枝节。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此人是专放高利贷的吸血鬼，心狠手辣，公卿大臣都不敢开罪他。最头痛是他手下能人无数，非常难应付。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈良兄你非常能干，得到这么多有用的消息，不知是否已查得大小姐的情人是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "我是信任张兄方肯透露一二，至于其他，张兄是明白人，请恕我要卖个关子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们最好衷诚合作，否则一个不好，不但完成不了主子吩咐的任务，还要死无全尸。唉！我宁愿开罪齐王，也不愿得罪仲孙龙。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_yun_er",
      "speaker_name": "雷允儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们闲着无事，想到街上逛逛，请管事赐准。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_lei_yun_er",
      "text": "我怎会阻各位去找乐子，记紧莫要生事，且天明前定要回来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你怎可答应他们，仲孙龙正虎视眈眈，说不定会拿他们来出气。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "时刻提心吊胆终不是办法，不过在大小姐演的两台歌舞之前，仲孙龙该不会生事。他怎都该给齐王和田单一点面子吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "齐襄王已老得糊涂，明明立了大王子田生为太子，却因小事把他废掉，弄得人心惶惶，现在仲孙龙正竭力举荐二王子田建为太子，与田单斗个不亦乐乎。今趟请来包括大小姐在内的三大名姬为齐王贺寿，是田单讨好襄王的手段，所以说不定仲孙龙会蓄意破坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 250,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 247
    }
  ],
